ighlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> flask <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Flask\napp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Flask<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__name__<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token decorator annotation punctuation\">@app<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;h1>Hello! World!&lt;/h1>\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> __name__ <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"__main__\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    app<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>run<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"플라스크-실행하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9D%BC%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"플라스크 실행하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>플라스크 실행하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Flask run</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>해당 파이썬 경로에서 이 명령어를 쳐주면 손쉽게 실행이 된다.\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45007556/99931839-6e608e80-2d99-11eb-98bd-721dff6bef54.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"확인하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"확인하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>확인하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>localhost:5000</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>해당 경로에 들어가서 Hello World! 메시지를 확인할 수 있다.\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45007556/99931902-9f40c380-2d99-11eb-9c4d-1637fba6e0e8.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"rest-api로-hello-world-출력하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rest-api%EB%A1%9C-hello-world-%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"rest api로 hello world 출력하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>REST API로 Hello World! 출력하기</h1>\n<h2 id=\"flask-restful-설치하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flask-restful-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"flask restful 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Flask-RESTful 설치하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>pip install flask-restful</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Flask는 이미 설치가 되어 있으니 Flask-RESTful만 추가로 설치해주면 된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"코드-작성하기-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-1\" aria-label=\"코드 작성하기 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>코드 작성하기</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> flask <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Flask\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> flask_restful <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Resource<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> reqparse<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Api\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HelloWorld</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Resource<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"World!\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span>\n\napp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Flask<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'My First App'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\napi <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Api<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>app<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\napi<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add_resource<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>HelloWorld<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/sayHello'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> __name__ <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'__main__'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    app<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>run<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>HelloWorld라는 클래스를 만들어주었는데, 이 때 메소드명을 get, post, put, delete 등으로 지어주면 자동으로 해당 요청 메소드로 매핑된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"플라스크-실행하기-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9D%BC%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-1\" aria-label=\"플라스크 실행하기 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>플라스크 실행하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>flask run</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>해당 파이썬 경로에서 이 명령어를 쳐주면 손쉽게 실행이 된다.\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45007556/99932130-7d940c00-2d9a-11eb-922e-65e404897d78.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"확인하기-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-1\" aria-label=\"확인하기 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>확인하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>localhost:5000/sayHello</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45007556/99932243-d82d6800-2d9a-11eb-8c07-8406bcec48c0.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"마지막으로\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EC%A7%80%EB%A7%89%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C\" aria-label=\"마지막으로 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>마지막으로</h1>\n<p>파이썬을 써보면서 너무 간편하고, 빠르게 여러 라이브러리를 사용해서 개발할 수 있다는 것에 매력을 느꼈는데, 플라스크는 그런 파이썬을 언어로 해서 가볍게 웹 개발을 할 수 있다는 점에서 매우 매력 있는 것 같다. 나중에 플라스크로 토이 프로젝트라도 해봐야 겠다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Flask 웹 프레임워크를 이용한 Hello World! 출력하기","date":"November 23, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020/2020-11-23-Flask-Hello/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/2020-11-21-ECMA-JavaScript/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ECMAScript? ES? 그게 뭘까?","category":"JavaScript","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/2020-11-24-Jekyll-redcarpet.md/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Jekyll 'Invalid Markdown processor given: redcarpet' 에러","category":"Error Log","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}